data.title: A History of Wonderful Inventions Parts 1-2
data.meta_description: New York: Harper & Brothers, Publishers, 1865. Reprint. Hardcover. 19.5 x 13 cm. 12mo. Two parts bound as one with seperate pagination, title pages, and frontispieces. 120pp, 126pp. Bound in brown cloth. In-text illustrations. Spine lettering is fading to illegibility. Gutter is cracked at page 24-25 of part 2. Bookplate on front fixed endpaper. Good. Item #72618
